findings.title: BT - Burn Tokens
findings.description: The contract owner has the authority to burn tokens from the contract’s total supply.

findings.title: UIF - Unlimited Increase Fees
findings.description: The contract owner has the authority to increase fees without limit.

findings.title: ST - Stop Transactions
findings.description: The contract owner has the authority to stop transactions for all users excluding the owner by setting the `_maxTxAmount` to zero.
